Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,Default,,0,0,2,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0}字幕调校: {\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&HCFE96F&\b0}星辰@CMCT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}电影真的很奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它是有自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果导演能拍出一部精彩作品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它肯定会比导演长命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}电影又很诡异
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}导演拍的东西想观众明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们偏偏看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有的没拍到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.29,0:00:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们却又看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有人说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}电影是导演的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.12,0:01:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实是导演创造了梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是梦创造了导演？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}停
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一 二 三 四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}五 六 七 八
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}导演
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回去看了你拍的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都不明白你在…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.29,0:02:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在…拍些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…我也搞不懂…你在说…说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…总是…要顶嘴…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…你什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知不知道 监制的权力比导演大？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只知道你说话结巴 不知道你哪样大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}九号是我的幸运号码
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每当我走到第九步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的灵感就会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可每到八步半 你就来打扰我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我正忙着拍戏呀 大监制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不要烦我行不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿妖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿妖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿妖 把那盏大灯给我挂上去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}照住大监制的头顶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}照醒他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:02:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}挂上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}挂上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}挂上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大监制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知不知道在拍摄现场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}导演的权力最大？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}轮不到你作主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿妖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}挂上去 照醒他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你…这样说话…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我现在就炒你鱿鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没力啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.83,0:03:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}监制 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事…没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}导演出事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}导演 导演…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}导演有事呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.63,0:03:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 导演晕倒了 - 怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 出什么事了？ - 召救护车 快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 怎么办？ - 导演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}导演有事呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 导演晕倒了 - 召救护车 导演晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}召救护车 快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.25,0:05:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是什么地方？我怎会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我成了鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这世界哪有鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的电影还没拍完 怎会上映呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里就是鸿图楼 不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们会给"人情"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有喜帖都不让进 什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是来喝喜酒 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别离开婆婆半步 听到吗？阿仔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里 斗大的字写着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鸿图楼楼上呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不就是嘛 鸿图楼楼上那层嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是来喝喜酒 又不是来打劫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就对了 楼上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿妹 这个适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一直都嫁不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}各位俊男美女 大家晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常开心 大家能够莅临东哥的喜宴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今晚 我们将在九大行星及嫦娥的见证下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起体验这对百年好合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事不宜迟 我们马上请大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稍移玉步到后面的回旋楼梯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慢慢升上来和大家一起用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 一个接一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不许插队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}七层楼 想累死人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.41,0:07:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大叔 多谢人情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么只给一千二百？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}两个人一千二 你开玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大叔 我们这儿有人情价目表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明码实价的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每个人头不低于五百块
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}八百块以下要自带椅子和饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的椅子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那请你进去时别占人家的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会吧 没有椅子 怎么吃呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我细鸡 只是帮东哥做兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有什么话直接跟东哥说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我怎么说也是阿东的三叔公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三叔公？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三叔公 请你快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要挡着街坊朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么急干什么 急着去死呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}插队？喝喜酒也要插队？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 肥姨 看来你会比他先饿死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我为什么会死？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很简单 你这儿才一份人情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你肯定要让给小孩吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样你还不饿死？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的孩子还不到一米五
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上大酒店吃东西都不用钱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你傻的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}企直 贴墙 抬高头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫你企直 抬高头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听不懂中文吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}婆婆教我 量身高时别站太直
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看到了 肥姨 过了一米五
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}政府是不是算一个人头？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}政府说的话你也相信？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}头发也算吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这不是超过一米五…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果头发也算 我恤起头发也比姚明高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}香港小姐头发那么长 竖起来不就两米多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}废话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是蛮横不讲理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那当然 看我这份量就是横着来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看到的 我是横着来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}换作是我就不收钱了 省点吧笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啊 怕你呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂…不能不收钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请留言…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请你吃榴莲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿东
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能不能快一点？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我给他剪了头发 你要给钱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么？你才四百？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你留着坐车回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}细鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记得把人情放进箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那边有个价目表 都给我核对好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟你说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你核对了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你今天好帅呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好位置在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}招呼不周 先打麻将
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}祝你百年好合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.70,0:10:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢 请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人情给了没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三年抱两
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢 这么大了 随便坐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那边才是好位…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}细鸡哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么事 东哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那妞到现在还不出现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不接电话 婚宴就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有新娘怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 这主意是我出的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可你才给我几天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一面要发帖邀请人来喝你的喜酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那边呢 还要帮你找个妞来充新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你指名道姓要那妞儿来做新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在她放你鸽子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这到底关我什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老大 现在是你欠人家钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别说了 现在没新娘 怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反正是假结婚 干嘛要那么认真？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现成有个妞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:10:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}长头发 大胸脯 厚嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你连我嫲嫲也叫来？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做戏做全套嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫲嫲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿东
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫲嫲真想不到 可以亲眼看着你娶媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我真的开心极了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你爸妈如果还在 也会很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我把你抚养成人到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最精彩就是今天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这玉镯是我给孙媳妇的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你快带我去见她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她人呢？我们去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她在补妆呀 嫲嫲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}趁她忙着补妆 我们打麻将等她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 先打麻将
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好呀 打麻将
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫲嫲交给我照顾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.54,0:12:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿东没跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 我打麻将 很出名的 - 谢谢 招呼不周 随便坐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}顺利邨第三座 分组第二名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么厉害 我是第四座冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过是帮我妈抽牌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三叔公 你喜欢摸就带两只回家摸个饱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对 是这只四索了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么多西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫲嫲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你老…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞什么鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}关公保佑 终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}牵住人家的手 见嫲嫲呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫲嫲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫲嫲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫲嫲 起床啦 嫲嫲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孙媳妇来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看 这件嫁衣是她亲手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多贤慧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就随便给封红包意思意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.25,0:13:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这水型人格的面相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.08,0:14:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚好可弥补阿东五行欠水的缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是天生夫妻相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给你红包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢嫲嫲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你叫什么名？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫多多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定会好好照顾阿东
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是皆大欢喜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们请便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}东哥 我还有点事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫲嫲 她不仅漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看她的屁股 就像我年轻时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肯定好生养
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了 刚才打电话给你 怎那么吵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打电话给我干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没什么 你一直不接电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有点害怕你会爽约
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我答应你就不会爽约
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚才 我回锦田的祖屋取这件嫁衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看 手工多精致
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我家传之宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那对龙爪好威猛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了 吃了这餐晚宴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚宴？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今晚有东西吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你等等 细鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃？才那么一丁点"人情"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫他们吃屎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就这么多人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是呀 你说你的亲戚都是稻草盖珍珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还说都是很阔绰 可都不来呀大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫他们吃屎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我真要吃屎了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}屎也得花钱买呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这回连屎也没得吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有个馊主意 保证比屎还便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么事呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要作弊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}举起双手 举起双手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吓鬼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你妨碍我干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}起火啦 火烧后巷呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火警 火警 快跑呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫲嫲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 当心点 - 嫲嫲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿东
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人都去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都走了 散席了 你回家休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你也早点休息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就只有一个乖孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要好好照顾他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}东哥 我送嫲嫲回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 等等 等等嫲嫲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}细鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫲嫲 我们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}细鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你觉得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像忘了样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会不会呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起 太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫲嫲 镯子你收好 不要给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给你的 你收好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别这样 嫲嫲 你留着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}过几天我们来看你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到时再给我们 好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不我来保管
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你觉得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得…最近真的好累
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}医生说我有肿瘤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么瘤 你死前可不可以先送我嫲嫲回家？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这没问题 你是大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫲嫲 我送你回家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}累了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚安 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 今晚别太累 - 再见嫲嫲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行啦 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}累了就找我来帮忙 知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}随便坐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这棵不就是蝎子凤梨 很罕见呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}识货 它叫秀莲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有那个 它叫秀月 中间的叫莹莹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最后面那棵叫茱安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你泡花呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有点感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抽烟？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少抽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}细鸡说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是他的老大 很能打
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}年轻时就能打
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在较多打飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在香港 做废青很难找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我打算先歇着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最近主要看看书 种些花草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你不就变成文化古惑仔？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实我也很喜欢种花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前还种了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过全都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我们可交流一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打算通宵跟我交流种花？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}细鸡说 今晚我们会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一条龙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实我很挑客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过看你这么帅 我也急着用钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你来我来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那…我先去洗个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你别这样急色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个人先洗也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是两个人洗澡有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是阿东老板？你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里是屯门警署
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}两小时前 锦田发生一宗车祸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}机主当场身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我见你是最后联络她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请问你是不是认识机主？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在方不方便过来认尸？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂？喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.83,0:21:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听见吗？喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}细鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大哥 大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那妞不是人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 知道… - 走走走…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.89,0:22:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的礼金呢？忘了在里面 陪我去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}礼金不要了 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拉的 你踢穿门干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这门开不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.83,0:22:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老大 你先跳楼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:22:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 老大怎能丢下你不管？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.75,0:23:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鬼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老大先跳楼 你马上跟着来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行 我抽出脚就跟你一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.33,0:23:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.58,0:23:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}礼金呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.25,0:24:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不是为了筹钱给我妈医病
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才不会跟你干这种缺德的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不算缺德
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不算？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.16,0:24:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那怎样才算？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.00,0:24:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫲嫲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.66,0:24:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是送你上小巴了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.33,0:24:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深更半夜很多坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.08,0:24:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我送你回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.66,0:24:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.79,0:24:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}骗我阿东
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.00,0:24:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老娘出来混的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.25,0:25:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你爸还在看蒙面超人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.45,0:25:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.62,0:25:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蠢蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.62,0:25:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爆啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.33,0:25:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.54,0:25:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}过来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.25,0:25:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}臭小子 乘人之危
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.83,0:25:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}专欺负无知少女 我警告你…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.66,0:25:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下次再遇上我 你就没这样好运
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.75,0:25:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.25,0:25:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多多
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.87,0:25:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.25,0:25:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你和阿东真的有缘份
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.66,0:25:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想想 香港有几百万人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.33,0:25:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们俩会一起假结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.00,0:25:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是天生一对
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.25,0:25:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等这件事过去后
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.04,0:25:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嫲嫲给你们搞一场最浪漫 最美丽的婚宴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.45,0:26:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}傻丫头 别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.33,0:26:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 嫲嫲 - 乖…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.66,0:26:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.00,0:26:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.33,0:26:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不结婚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.04,0:26:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先生 查票
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.54,0:26:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我…我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.37,0:26:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.50,0:27:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.58,0:27:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明卖出五张票 怎么会有七个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.66,0:27:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那两个人呢？还没查
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.04,0:27:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是不是在做梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.79,0:27:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就别停
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.70,0:27:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有灵感了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.75,0:27:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.16,0:27:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去吃屎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.45,0:27:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知不知道 你现在做每件事我都不满意
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.79,0:27:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.16,0:27:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是比我勤力
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.29,0:27:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你以为做得久比我勤力就行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.95,0:27:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是不明白 明白你就坐我位子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.12,0:27:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在这里我最大
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.91,0:28:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看外面有谁肯帮你？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.04,0:28:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很恼火？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.08,0:28:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会炒你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.70,0:28:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会慢慢折磨你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.62,0:28:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也休想辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.91,0:28:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}负资产怎供楼 露宿街头呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.50,0:28:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出去干活
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.54,0:28:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}滚
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.29,0:28:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.66,0:28:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}关门
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.20,0:28:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫你女朋友进来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.83,0:28:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梁震找你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.20,0:29:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}废物
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.04,0:29:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫你呀 范知进
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.79,0:29:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把明天开会要用的东西搬上会议室
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.45,0:29:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天你不用来了 会议没你的份
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.41,0:29:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个人搬 别妨碍其他同事工作
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.75,0:29:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}电梯又坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.87,0:29:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走楼梯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.83,0:32:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.62,0:32:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道你想怎样 你是比我勤力
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.33,0:32:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这里做的也比我久
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.12,0:32:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会炒你 我会慢慢折磨你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.70,0:32:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么多大厦 想砸死人呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.58,0:32:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.87,0:32:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.41,0:32:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你从那座大厦下来是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.54,0:32:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.16,0:32:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知不知道 每座大厦的窗门后面
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.37,0:32:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有很多秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.25,0:33:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你都神…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.00,0:33:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎么知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.04,0:33:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我真的是神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.16,0:33:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 我给你些种子 - 喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.87,0:33:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 开花你就发啦 - 你干什么…干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.66,0:33:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}神经病
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.66,0:34:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我给你些种子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.41,0:34:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开花你就发啦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.37,0:36:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.79,0:36:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小子 超重了 出去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.58,0:36:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大叔 别这么凶 斯文点
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.91,0:36:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}斯文点？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.95,0:36:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在就是你们这些小子搞得香港乱哄哄
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.45,0:36:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不说是你们老不死的在挡路
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.70,0:36:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老不死？信不信我找你妈打醒你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.04,0:36:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开玩笑 吓唬我呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.00,0:36:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就打你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.37,0:36:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打我？吃屎吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.95,0:36:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敢还手？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.25,0:36:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让一让…请让一让…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.20,0:36:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让开
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.83,0:36:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别妨碍警察办案
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.25,0:36:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我倒杯水给你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.33,0:36:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}樱桃为何会这么狠？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.29,0:36:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很恐怖呀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.37,0:37:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是呀 她一刀在颈部割下去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.16,0:37:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎能下手？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.70,0:37:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们早回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.00,0:37:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}见她拿着老板送给她的订情礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.54,0:37:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要退还给他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.87,0:37:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接着两位便在房内吵起来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.20,0:37:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想是老板求爱不遂而霸王硬上弓
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.20,0:37:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他…强奸我
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.45,0:39:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}范知进
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.62,0:39:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不认得我声音了？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.29,0:40:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死啦…死啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.41,0:40:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}王后
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.29,0:40:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死啦…死了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.00,0:40:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看什么 我又不是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.16,0:40:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女人好烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.29,0:40:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 如果她喜欢你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.20,0:40:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是挺可爱…的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.75,0:41:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿进
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.50,0:41:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梁震疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.41,0:41:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他割伤自己的脸之后
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.66,0:41:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从医院跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.04,0:41:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他不肯放过我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.08,0:41:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他还没死？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.75,0:41:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这条钥匙我一直留着
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.37,0:41:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得 我来这里会安全点
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.20,0:41:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是我的 你为什么要走？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.50,0:43:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿进 我报警了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.50,0:43:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你见过公司附近的隧道那个乞丐？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.37,0:43:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听说 他是公司老员工
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.95,0:44:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被前老板逼走后就疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.95,0:44:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}挺多人捧场
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.62,0:44:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不错
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.54,0:44:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.95,0:45:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}儿童图书里
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.00,0:45:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很多时候 王子和公主都有美满结局
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.45,0:45:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但现实是不是这样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.04,0:45:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这问是我的祖屋
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.12,0:45:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是我成为插画家的源头
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.50,0:51:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 陈老板
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.16,0:51:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 对不起 我最近有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.37,0:51:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道 但真的有点私人事情
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.45,0:51:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能不能再给我几天时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.37,0:51:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会尽快给你
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.33,0:51:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.16,0:51:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.95,0:54:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老婆 生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.04,0:54:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很惊喜吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.79,0:54:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我不好 迟了给你庆祝
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.62,0:54:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在给你补上 你别生气
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.79,0:54:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我生日那天你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.50,0:54:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟你说过嘛 我陪了一个客户
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.33,0:54:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你陪的不是客户
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.50,0:54:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟她没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.45,0:54:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她有钱可以帮我 就这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.33,0:54:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且那次以后 我再没见过她了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.33,0:54:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我什么都看见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.37,0:55:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我什么都看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.04,0:55:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.87,0:55:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这十年来 我这样辛苦为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.16,0:55:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还不是为了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.87,0:55:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道就没回转余地？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.62,0:55:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不过做错了一次
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.91,0:55:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道你帮了我不少
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.54,0:55:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我在外面真的欠了人家很多钱
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.20,0:55:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想你再勉强接那么多工作
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.08,0:55:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.04,0:55:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不知道怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.33,0:55:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老婆 你再帮我这一次
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.00,0:55:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这房子 反正你很久都没回来住
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.87,0:55:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}卖掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.25,0:55:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}卖掉它 我们可以像以前那样开心
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.04,0:55:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你说没见过她？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.00,0:56:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没见过她 这香水味从哪里来？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.75,0:56:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在哄我卖房子 好让你有钱花？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.16,0:56:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底骗了我多少次？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.75,0:56:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 你骗了我多少次 你说 - 你发什么疯
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.12,0:56:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你别这样 老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.87,0:56:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我发疯是吗 你走
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.70,0:56:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.87,0:56:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老婆
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.95,1:03:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.58,1:03:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好想你
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.12,1:03:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道你在这
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.29,1:03:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你出来见我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.16,1:04:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救命啊 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.12,1:05:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}邓祁山 你想怎样？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.37,1:05:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你干什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.87,1:05:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放开我
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.50,1:05:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这地方这么值钱你都不卖
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.12,1:05:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会痛 很快的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.12,1:05:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.37,1:05:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}邓祁山你不是人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.37,1:05:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放开我
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.70,1:05:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见 老婆
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.00,1:05:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放开我 你不是人
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.54,1:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乖女
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.04,1:06:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.16,1:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈没有好好照顾你
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.83,1:06:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}里面那男人这样对你
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.37,1:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会放过他
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.66,1:06:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.08,1:06:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.58,1:06:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别丢下我…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.12,1:06:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回来啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.33,1:07:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这工厂是我婆婆留给我妈
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.00,1:07:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我妈再留给我
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.62,1:07:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我做自己喜欢做的事有什么问题？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.54,1:07:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总之 你爱打棉胎你自己打个够
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.45,1:07:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打到死那天我也不会再理你
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.25,1:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不要骗我
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.54,1:08:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道你外面有女人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.29,1:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}神经病 我不跟你啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.41,1:08:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去死吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.25,1:08:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}着火啦…
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.79,1:08:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救命啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.50,1:09:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来 王子是魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.54,1:09:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在千钧一发时 病危的母后及时赶到
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.95,1:09:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母后拼死和魔鬼同归于尽
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.79,1:09:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伟大的母爱终于救了小公主
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.58,1:09:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彤彤 你肯回来孤儿院教书
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.58,1:09:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很开心
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.58,1:09:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}应该的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.70,1:09:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}院长
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.25,1:09:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这本是我画的新作 送给你
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.87,1:09:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望你喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.37,1:09:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.37,1:10:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.41,1:10:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}关二哥在上 我们五子遭逢厄运
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.29,1:10:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要有一位死士 以身犯险
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.91,1:10:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恳请关二哥 抽这位死士出来
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.41,1:10:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜过关二哥 大家莫啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.62,1:10:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我跟关二哥不太熟
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.41,1:10:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只知道他喜欢听我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.25,1:10:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我现在去厕所再唱
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.04,1:10:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁慢谁吃亏
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.45,1:10:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明说好抽签
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.87,1:10:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抢什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.12,1:10:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是 现在还不是一人一枝？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.20,1:10:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}浪费口水
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.54,1:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家拿出来对一对
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.29,1:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁人抽了死签？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.66,1:10:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么死签？都一样长
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.04,1:10:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有说过比长短吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.41,1:10:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吓？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.83,1:10:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.20,1:10:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没事
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.83,1:10:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你呀…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.04,1:10:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我扭不了？为什么…
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.16,1:10:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就扭得了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.95,1:11:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你呀
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.75,1:11:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大老板 我们抽了生死签了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.29,1:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}关二哥决定 阿聪走东城线
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.04,1:11:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没这回事
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.00,1:11:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}关二哥？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.75,1:11:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我推翻这个决定
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.00,1:11:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们是一间大公司
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.41,1:11:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么能用这种迷信的方式呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.70,1:11:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 我决定…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.08,1:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}投票
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.58,1:11:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就你了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.37,1:11:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我们先出去
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.04,1:11:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不去
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.50,1:11:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.45,1:11:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}东城戏院那条线 停了十几年呀
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.12,1:11:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.75,1:11:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}东城电影院 以前是个殡仪馆嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.86,1:11:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道还要我去？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.50,1:12:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿聪 我跟你讲
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.62,1:12:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们可以来一个…
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.04,1:12:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"撞鬼自游行"
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.50,1:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刺激呀 我把他们一车一车的拉去撞鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.37,1:12:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}钱就一车一车的来
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.54,1:12:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们还集资上市干什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.16,1:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咱们直奔纳斯达克
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.66,1:12:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自游不行
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.95,1:12:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不知道 好多前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.25,1:12:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去了那边 都…失踪呀
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.91,1:12:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}司机找到了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.79,1:12:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他老婆对他不好 离家出走
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.20,1:12:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不去
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.37,1:12:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你前几天是不是请假？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.24,1:12:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要去参加什么唱歌比赛？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.87,1:12:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对呀 对呀 参加比赛
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.77,1:12:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我买个新吉他 三万多啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.06,1:12:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去不上了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.29,1:12:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.16,1:12:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我不给你假呀
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.16,1:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老板呀 你给我机会呀
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.66,1:12:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道我唱歌多好听啊 我唱给你听啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.22,1:13:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是否你唯一的粉肠
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.45,1:13:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感动吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.45,1:13:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感动
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.00,1:13:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好不好听？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.12,1:13:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好听
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.83,1:13:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难受吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.25,1:13:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难受 你…
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.41,1:13:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你到底是想穷死 还是想吓死？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.41,1:13:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我这个人 是个公平 公正 公开的人
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.79,1:13:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里有个球
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.33,1:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我把它投进篮里
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.58,1:13:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算我赢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.45,1:13:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去东城
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.75,1:13:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我投不进去呢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.91,1:13:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你赢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.66,1:13:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不去 好不好？
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.33,1:13:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不公平
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.16,1:13:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以的 来
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.95,1:13:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢老板
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.50,1:13:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样也投不进去
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.95,1:13:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老板 你好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.79,1:13:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老板好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.41,1:14:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了减低公司损失的风险
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.91,1:14:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们精心挑选公司最破的一辆车
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.75,1:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去迎接这个九死一生的任务
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.54,1:14:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我真的舍不得…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.41,1:14:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这辆车
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.00,1:14:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有心
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.33,1:14:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我送个对话机给你
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.16,1:14:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有心
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.00,1:14:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}二十四小时都要保持联络
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.45,1:14:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我怕万一你有什么事…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.54,1:14:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}起码我们也知道 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.16,1:14:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}家属谢礼
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.50,1:14:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一路走好
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.29,1:15:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.37,1:15:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"南无阿弥陀佛…"
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.04,1:15:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 换别的音乐行不行？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.62,1:15:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.29,1:16:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 开
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.58,1:16:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会吧 真的十五个五？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.00,1:16:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蠢材 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.33,1:16:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我蠢？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.58,1:16:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿聪一把年纪 还在做歌星梦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.12,1:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他才真蠢呀
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.91,1:16:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少废话 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.87,1:16:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喝就喝
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.66,1:16:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 再来
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.78,1:16:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.41,1:16:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回应一下好吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.15,1:16:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.54,1:16:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.66,1:16:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 来点动静呀
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.73,1:16:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂喂喂 别闹了 真的怕
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.83,1:17:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大哥 真害怕呀
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.29,1:17:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有个阿婆在车上
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.54,1:17:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救命…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.91,1:17:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救命啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.37,1:17:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.29,1:17:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是肾
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.20,1:17:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下面是屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.41,1:17:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿婆 你别乱戳
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.50,1:17:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是说 这是什么站呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.75,1:17:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是东院坟场
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.87,1:17:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿婆 你想在哪里下车？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.04,1:17:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我到家啦
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.87,1:18:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吓得我…
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.45,1:18:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小伙子
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.41,1:18:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.91,1:18:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你车上有脏东西
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.12,1:18:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你自己小心呀
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.79,1:18:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么多家人
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.20,1:18:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都出来等
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.66,1:18:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事吧 阿婆？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.87,1:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}住这里？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.91,1:18:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爬这么高 回天国？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.20,1:18:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心跳出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.16,1:18:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想尿尿
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.33,1:18:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们这些混蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.16,1:18:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有瓶子
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.41,1:18:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样瞧得起我 这么窄？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.25,1:18:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.62,1:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}窄点也好 试试
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.20,1:18:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.62,1:19:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么窄用不得 有进无出
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.79,1:19:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有人吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.54,1:19:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不对
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.91,1:19:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.66,1:19:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起 我的妈…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.62,1:19:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有怪莫怪 小孩尿急尿过界
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.62,1:19:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鬼呀
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.00,1:19:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死啦…救命啊
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.54,1:19:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}按不住啦…
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.41,1:19:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你个混蛋 在我花园尿尿？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.75,1:20:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 等等…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.58,1:20:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}司机大哥 满地都是水 怎么搞的？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.45,1:20:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}随便啦 又没让你喝
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.87,1:20:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好面熟
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.62,1:20:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在哪里见过呢？看着我
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.04,1:20:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没见过帅哥呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.62,1:20:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.00,1:20:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还让你认出来
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.41,1:20:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我认得你啦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.20,1:20:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一把年纪 年年都参加歌唱比赛
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.62,1:20:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}年年都怯场的那位大叔？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.66,1:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你才一把年纪
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.62,1:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来你开巴士？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.25,1:20:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很失礼你吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.29,1:20:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了 我记得你唱那首歌
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.41,1:20:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好正点 这样的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.87,1:20:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"我是否你唯一的粉肠"
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.91,1:20:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唱够没有
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.12,1:20:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的很趣致 真的
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.29,1:20:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}滚开吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.70,1:20:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没人看见 玩玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.62,1:21:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先生 你车上有脏东西
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.33,1:21:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也看到了？快走
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.66,1:21:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.62,1:21:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也是？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.41,1:21:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救命啊
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.63,1:21:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你哭什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.12,1:22:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她掐住我伤口
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.83,1:22:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别哭了 男人老狗
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.79,1:22:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们在哪里下车呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.58,1:22:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们去总站 东城戏院
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.83,1:22:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真以为我们是女鬼呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.79,1:22:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们是乐队
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.50,1:22:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是来参加化妆舞会
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.66,1:22:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是为了庆祝这巴士线重开而举办
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.20,1:22:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来吧 快些和我们一起进场玩
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.91,1:22:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜托
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.41,1:22:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地板那么脏 有人呕吐就找人清洁呀
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.79,1:22:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走吧 迟到啦
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.08,1:22:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}改天吧 你…你先走
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.45,1:22:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.95,1:23:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你先走 改天再约
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.41,1:23:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别这样 可以上台唱歌 你唱得那么好听
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.45,1:23:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别耍我了 我哪会唱歌
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.62,1:23:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要谦虚 你唱歌很好听
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.66,1:23:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.66,1:23:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唱什么歌？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.04,1:23:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唱什么歌？我们给你伴奏
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.75,1:23:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们给你伴奏？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.87,1:23:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎那么啰嗦？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.91,1:23:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是什么歌呀？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.75,1:23:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.25,1:23:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁唱的？没听过？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.70,1:23:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快开始了
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.45,1:23:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}入场啦
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.41,1:24:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"都黐咗线走火入魔 鬼怪甚多"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.75,1:24:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"问你怕不怕"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.25,1:24:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"哎呀弊啦 佢扮傻（佢系坚傻）"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.83,1:24:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"惊乜鬼一于少理继续唱歌"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.79,1:24:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"唱到劲跳热舞 齐齐变成舞王 八步半"
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.70,1:25:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"世界话变就变 人人芝麻开门 八步半"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.70,1:25:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"八个十个伴唱 齐齐唱齐唱齐"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.16,1:25:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"继续唱 继续跳 八步八步八步半"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.12,1:25:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"咁鬼人齐 应该皆大欢喜"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.58,1:25:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"但系点解你哋个个都好似就死"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.41,1:25:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"有啲黐埋一坺"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.20,1:25:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"其他甩头甩脾"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.70,1:25:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"医番好都嘥气"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.16,1:25:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"叫晒佢哋番屋企"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.91,1:25:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"点算左眼好似望到孖女齐坐"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.33,1:25:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"望下似幻觉"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.83,1:25:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"哎呀弊啦 我系傻（系个呀婆）"
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.41,1:25:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"惊乜鬼惊都嘥气继续唱歌"
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.70,1:26:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}导演 你好
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.66,1:26:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好…唱得很好…
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.16,1:26:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.33,1:26:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个顽皮妹
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.16,1:26:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小姐 这是男厕所
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.33,1:26:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救命啊 我见鬼啦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.66,1:26:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是不是像我们这样？
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.04,1:27:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}

